items.description: Logical interconnect group for bays 1,2,3,4,5 and 6.

issues.description: The selected enclosure's Virtual Connect configuration does not match the selected OneView logical interconnect group "LIG_2SN44000VW_1". The follow uplinkset "up_Bay1" from existing logical interconnect group "LIG_2SN44000VW_1" are not present in the Virtual Connect configuration. They must match in size, name, and configuration.
issues.recommendation: Modify the selected enclosure's Virtual Connect configuration or the specified OneView logical interconnect group "LIG_2SN44000VW_1" to be consistent. After the modifications are complete, retry the operation.

issues.description: The selected enclosure's Virtual Connect configuration does not match the selected OneView logical interconnect group "LIG_2SN44000VW_1". The uplinkset "up_Bay1X" from the Virtual Connect configuration did not match one in the existing logical interconnect group "LIG_2SN44000VW_1". They must match in name, number of uplinks, and configuration.
issues.recommendation: Modify the selected enclosure's Virtual Connect configuration or modify OneView logical interconnect group "LIG_2SN44000VW_1" to be consistent. After the modifications are complete, retry the operation.
